***Procedure installation Arma tools/Buldozer/ObjectBuilder***
-Telecharger et lancer Arma3 Tools (en ayant choisit la dev build et activé les MAJ automatiques)
-Monter le lecteur P "mount the project drive"
-Le dossier armaproject se créera automatiquement dans les documents
-Importation des dossiers du dossier racine du jeu "project drive management" -> "ExtractGame Data"
-






-Remplacement des dll presents par ceux de la racine du jeu
-Installation Buldozer
-Dans ArmaTools preferences  regler et creer fichier config
-Ouverture object builder

***Configuration***
-dans fichiers/options 
-External Viewer: P:\buldozer.exe -buldozer -name=Buldozer -window -noLand -exThreads=0 -noLogs -noAsserts -cfg=p:\buldozer.cfg
DLL Folder: <steamPath>\steamapps\common\Arma 3 Tools\ObjectBuilder
(replace <SteamPath> with the full path to your Steam directory), in the end, this must points the root directory of Object Builder.
Path for textures: P:\ 

ouvrir terrain builder
- Open Terrain Builder, go into “Tools” >> “Preferences”
Set the following parameters:
a3ct terrainBuilder options.jpg

.exe file path: P:\Buldozer.exe
Launch parameters: -buldozer -name=Buldozer -window -exThreads=0 -disableSteam -noAsserts -cfg=p:\buldozer.cfg
Data Directory: P:\
